FBIS4-16417 "drsov074_p_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Deputy Shot, Killed in Yerevan Deputy Shot, Killed in Yerevan NC1504203894 Yerevan Armenia's Radio First Program Network in Armenian 1950 GMT 15 Apr 94 NC1504203894 Yerevan Armenia's Radio First Program Network in Armenian 1950 GMT 15 Apr 94 Armenian BFN [Text] The Armenian parliamentarian, writer, and public speaker Vardges Petrosyan was killed by (?a single) shot fired by unidentified persons at around 1700 today at the entrance of his residence on Khorenatsi Street on his return from work. The Armenian Interior Ministry press service reported that Interior Minister Vano Siradegyan has gone to the site of the incident with an operations team. The public prosecutor and the inspector at the public prosecutor's office in Spandaryan district have also gone there. A criminal investigation has been launched and it is being conducted by the public prosecutor's office in Spandaryan district.
